# akka_service (Data Source)

Reads an existing Akka service by name within a project. Use this data source to reference a
service that was deployed outside of Terraform.

## Example Usage

```hcl
data "akka_service" "api" {
  name    = "api-service"
  project = "production"
}

output "api_hostname" {
  value = data.akka_service.api.hostname
}
```

